<body>
<cb:div>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0253a" xml:id="I01.0095.0253a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0253a00" type="honorific"/><cb:docNumber>No. 95</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0253a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>唐邕刻經記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0253a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0253a0101">粵若稽古。逖聽風聲。握神紀以應物。遊靈教而至道者有矣。咸弘之在人。道不虛泄。然則
<lb ed="I" n="0253a02" type="honorific"/>軒從七聖。蘭葉傳文。舜共三公。芝泥觀字。周朝關令。望東氣而稽首。<note n="0253001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31127"/>＝丘【史】</note><note n="0253001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31127"/>【佛拓】，丘【史】</note><app n="0253001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">丘</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31127"/></rdg></app>門弟子。向北斗而
<lb ed="I" n="0253a03" type="honorific"/>磬折。天書道記。可略言也。蓋不出於九流。且未聞於三世。我　　大齊之君。區有義□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">不</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0253a04" type="honorific"/>思。家傳天帝之尊。世祚輪王之貴。一人示見。百辟應生。俯順龜龍。託迹雲火。翠鳳將寶幢
<lb ed="I" n="0253a05" type="honorific"/>共舉。靈鼉與<note n="0253002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">灋＝法【史】</note><note n="0253002" resp="ihp" type="mod">灋【佛拓】，法【史】</note><app n="0253002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">法</lem><rdg wit="【原】">灋</rdg></app>鼓俱震。萬機兼十<note n="0253003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">譱＝善【史】</note><note n="0253003" resp="ihp" type="mod">譱【佛拓】，善【史】</note><app n="0253003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">善</lem><rdg wit="【原】">譱</rdg></app>之化。四門雜三乘之賓。自迦葉結集。蔡愔遊返。持綖
<lb ed="I" n="0253a06" type="honorific"/>之經。盛於茲日。龍宮斯盡。<note n="0253004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB07782"/>＝象【史】</note><note n="0253004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB07782"/>【佛拓】，象【史】</note><app n="0253004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">象</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB07782"/></rdg></app>載未勝。特進驃騎大將軍開府儀同三司尚書令并州大中
<lb ed="I" n="0253a07" type="honorific"/>正食司州濮陽郡幹長安縣開國侯<note n="0253005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB07778"/>＝晉【史】</note><note n="0253005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB07778"/>【佛拓】，晉【史】</note><app n="0253005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">晉</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB07778"/></rdg></app>昌郡開國公唐邕。挺固理時。生而為世。秉文<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">經</unclear>武。
<lb ed="I" n="0253a08" type="honorific"/>來處<note n="0253006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">庿＝廟【史】</note><note n="0253006" resp="ihp" type="mod">庿【佛拓】，廟【史】</note><app n="0253006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">廟</lem><rdg wit="【原】">庿</rdg></app>堂。從扣而鳴。隨病與藥。待群方而似鏡。應眾<note n="0253007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31117"/>＝務【史】</note><note n="0253007" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31117"/>【佛拓】，務【史】</note><app n="0253007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">務</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31117"/></rdg></app><note n="0253008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30720"/>＝其【史】</note><note n="0253008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30720"/>【佛拓】，其【史】</note><app n="0253008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">其</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30720"/></rdg></app>如響。四海仰以彌高。千官挹而
<lb ed="I" n="0253a09" type="honorific"/>滿<note n="0253009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31118"/>＝腹【史】</note><note n="0253009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31118"/>【佛拓】，腹【史】</note><app n="0253009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">腹</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31118"/></rdg></app>。眷言法寶。是所歸依。以為縑緗有壞。簡策非久。金牒難求。皮紙易滅。於是發七處之
<lb ed="I" n="0253a10" type="honorific"/>印。開七寶之函。訪蓮華之書。命銀鉤之迹。一音所說。盡勒名山。於鼓山石窟之所。寫維<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">摩</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0253a11" type="honorific"/>詰經一部。勝鬘經一部。孛經一部。彌勒成佛經一部。起天統四年三月一日。盡武平三年
<lb ed="I" n="0253a12" type="honorific"/>歲次壬辰五月廿八日。<note n="0253010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB00117"/>＝澗【史】</note><note n="0253010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB00117"/>【佛拓】，澗【史】</note><app n="0253010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">澗</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB00117"/></rdg></app>谷虛靜。邑居閑曠。林疑極妙。艸匹文柔。禽繞空中。獸依樹下。水
<lb ed="I" n="0253a13" type="honorific"/>音發而覺道。風響動而悟物。戒行之徒允<note n="0253011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">雧＝集【史】</note><note n="0253011" resp="ihp" type="mod">雧【佛拓】，集【史】</note><app n="0253011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">集</lem><rdg wit="【原】">雧</rdg></app>。慧定之侶攸歸。如日貫雲。常轉不息。□非恐
<lb ed="I" n="0253a14" type="honorific"/>畏。未苦風寒。石比夜光。非待<note n="0253012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31119"/>＝螢【史】</note><note n="0253012" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31119"/>【佛拓】，螢【史】</note><app n="0253012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">螢</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31119"/></rdg></app>雪。毗沙上度。敕眾鬼而護持。大梵來遊。領群神而<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">保</unclear>衛。<app type="star" corresp="#0253003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">善</lem><rdg wit="【原】">譱</rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0253a15" type="honorific"/>因<note n="0253013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31120"/>＝普【史】</note><note n="0253013" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31120"/>【佛拓】，普【史】</note><app n="0253013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">普</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31120"/></rdg></app>被。願力薰脩。當使世界同於淨土。　皇基固於大地。<note n="0253014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31121"/>＝置【史】</note><note n="0253014" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31121"/>【佛拓】，置【史】</note><app n="0253014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">置</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31121"/></rdg></app>六道於十山。沐四生於八□。
<lb ed="I" n="0253a16" type="honorific"/>乃及無邊。皆取正覺。海收經籍。斯文必傳。山從水火。此方無壞。重宣茲義。乃作銘曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0253a17" type="honorific"/>天文<note n="0253015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31122"/>＝星【史】</note><note n="0253015" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31122"/>【佛拓】，星【史】</note><app n="0253015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">星</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31122"/></rdg></app>象。人文書契。先聖後賢。道纔身世。惟　皇建國。教通群藝。德實無為。化窮兼<note n="0253016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB09497"/>＝濟【史】</note><note n="0253016" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB09497"/>【佛拓】，濟【史】</note><app n="0253016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">濟</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB09497"/></rdg></app>。諸
<lb ed="I" n="0253a18" type="honorific"/>法為祖。諸經亦王。一文半偈。與物行<note n="0253017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">蔵＝藏【史】</note><note n="0253017" resp="ihp" type="mod">蔵【佛拓】，藏【史】</note><app n="0253017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">藏</lem><rdg wit="【原】">蔵</rdg></app>。天縱上士。時應有方。群迷升極。至道津梁。殺青有
<lb ed="I" n="0253a19" type="honorific"/><note n="0253018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31123"/>＝缺【史】</note><note n="0253018" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31123"/>【佛拓】，缺【史】</note><app n="0253018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">缺</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31123"/></rdg></app>。韋編有絕。一託貞堅。永<note n="0253019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31124"/>＝垂【史】</note><note n="0253019" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31124"/>【佛拓】，垂【史】</note><app n="0253019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">垂</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31124"/></rdg></app>昭<note n="0253020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">晣＝晰【史】</note><note n="0253020" resp="ihp" type="mod">晣【佛拓】，晰【史】</note><app n="0253020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">晰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">晣</rdg></app>。天神左右。天王<note n="0253021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31126"/>＝擁【史】</note><note n="0253021" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31126"/>【佛拓】，擁【史】</note><app n="0253021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">擁</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31126"/></rdg></app>衛。書未仙遊。字無飛滅。地遙常寂。山
<lb ed="I" n="0253a20" type="honorific"/>空避喧。承風覺道。海渧難論。水流可閱。日去無翻乘茲誓願。福地常存。</p>
